$TMHC $BRK.A $BRK.B Berkshire is making a move.  

Berkshire Hathaway to Acquire Taylor Morrison Home Corporation for $8.5 Billion  

&quot;Taylor Morrison Home Corporation (NYSE:TMHC) and Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (NYSE:BRK, BRK.B)) jointly announced today that they have reached a definitive agreement for Berkshire Hathaway to acquire Taylor Morrison for $72.50 per common share in cash, representing a total equity value for Taylor Morrison of approximately $6.8 billion and total enterprise value of approximately $8.5 billion. The acquisition price represents a 24% premium to Taylor Morrison&#39;s latest closing price of $58.50 on May 29, 2026.&quot;

